---
title: Turmeric Lamb Curry with Coconut Milk
description: Aromatics are the key to a flavourful curry. Tonight's curry is packed with ginger, fennel seeds, cumin and turmeric. Savoury lamb and rich coconut milk balance out this bright yellow curry!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-dagneau-au-curcuma-8e4e7cf4.jpg
